import * as React from 'react' import Paginacao from '../componentes/paginacao' import Cards from '../componentes/cards' import axios from 'axios' import { BASE_URL } from '../utils/requests' import { ImovelPage } from '../types/imovel' export default function Listing() { const [pageNumber, setPageNumber] =React.useState(0) const [page, setPage] = React.useState( { content: [], last: true, totalPages: 0, totalElements: 0, size: 12, number: 0, first: true, numberOfElements: 0, empty: true } ) React.useEffect(()=>{ axios.get(`${BASE_URL}/imovel?size=12&page=${pageNumber}`) .then(response => { const data = response.data as ImovelPage setPage(data) }) }, [page]) return ( <>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
) }
